&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Intradepartmental mentor and buddy program for in-house networking&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;An inclusive company culture, ability to join our Community Guilds (Datadog employee resource groups)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
