&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have been designing and engineering UIs for several years&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re a master of the Javascript ecosystem and you’re aware of the latest trends with frontend technologies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
