&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;You’re excited about leveraging AI tools to enhance how you code, solve problems, and build – or eager to learn how&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
